snippet: Brandt Snedeker played bogey-free at Spyglass Hill on Friday for a five-under-par 67 to share the 36-hole lead with Matt Jones in the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am.
abstract: Brandt Snedeker shoots five-under-par 67 to share lead with Matt Jones in Pebble Beach Pro-Am; other golf news noted.
